{"id":"939fe9a5ea89","content":"Capacity is one of the hardest problems because it sits at the knotty, gnarled-up intersection of so many other hard problems.​​​​‌﻿‍﻿​‍​‍‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‌﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿‍​‍​‍​﻿‍‍​‍​‍‌﻿​﻿‌‍​‌‌‍﻿‍‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌​‍﻿‍‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿﻿​‍​‍​‍﻿​​‍​‍‌‍‍​‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‌‌‍‌‍​‍​‍​﻿‍‍​‍​‍‌‍‍​‌﻿‌​‌﻿‌​‌﻿​​‌﻿​﻿​﻿‍‍​‍﻿﻿​‍﻿﻿‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿‌‌﻿​﻿​‍﻿‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‍﻿‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿﻿​‍﻿﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​‌‍‌‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​​‍﻿﻿‌‍‌‌‌‍‌​‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌​​‍﻿﻿‌‍﻿‌‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌﻿​​‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‌‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿﻿‌‍﻿‍​﻿‍﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍‌​​﻿﻿‌​﻿​‍​﻿​﻿‌‍‌‌​﻿​‌​﻿‍‌​﻿‌​​﻿‍​‌‍‌‍​‍﻿‌‌‍‌‍‌‍​﻿‌‍​‌​﻿​​​‍﻿‌​﻿‌​​﻿‌​‌‍‌​​﻿‍​​‍﻿‌‌‍​‌‌‍​﻿‌‍​﻿​﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‌​﻿​​​﻿​﻿‌‍‌​​﻿‌‌​﻿​‍‌‍‌‌​﻿‌‌‌‍‌‌​﻿‌‌‌‍​‍​﻿‌‌‌‍‌‌​﻿‍﻿‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌﻿‌‌​​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​​﻿‍﻿‌﻿​​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌‌‌﻿‍​‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​​‌﻿‌​​﻿﻿﻿‌‍​‍‌‍​‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‌‌‌‌‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍﻿​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‍​‌﻿‌​‌﻿‌​‌﻿​​‌﻿​﻿​‍‌‌​﻿​﻿‌​​‌​‍‌‌​﻿​‍‌​‌‍​‍‌‌​﻿​‍‌​‌‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿‌‌﻿​﻿​‍﻿‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‍﻿‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‌​​﻿﻿‌​﻿​‍​﻿​﻿‌‍‌‌​﻿​‌​﻿‍‌​﻿‌​​﻿‍​‌‍‌‍​‍﻿‌‌‍‌‍‌‍​﻿‌‍​‌​﻿​​​‍﻿‌​﻿‌​​﻿‌​‌‍‌​​﻿‍​​‍﻿‌‌‍​‌‌‍​﻿‌‍​﻿​﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‌​﻿​​​﻿​﻿‌‍‌​​﻿‌‌​﻿​‍‌‍‌‌​﻿‌‌‌‍‌‌​﻿‌‌‌‍​‍​﻿‌‌‌‍‌‌​‍‌‍‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌﻿‌‌​​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​​‍‌‍‌﻿​​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌‌‌﻿‍​‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​​‌﻿‌​​‍‌‍‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌‌‍​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌﻿​​‌﻿‌‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍‍‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‍​‌‍‌‌‌‍‌​​‍​‍‌﻿﻿‌"}